#TRIGGER {A loud thud can be heard from the storage compartment as trash is depositted by the collectors.} {#gagline ALL; #Play {Prometheus\General\collecting\TrashThump.wav} @Vol; #If {@PanTrash = 1} {#PC %PlayHandle Pan %random(-4000,4000)}} {}
#TRIGGER {The floor beneath your feet begins rumbling softly as the refinery is activated.} {#gagline ALL; #Play {Prometheus\Ship\Misc\constructionFacilityPowerUp.wav} @Vol} {}
